Store index.mdwn files in a directory hierachy. Store the style.css, [header.inc](https://github.com/kaihendry/sg-hackandtell/blob/master/header.inc) & [footer.inc](https://github.com/kaihendry/sg-hackandtell/blob/master/footer.inc) in the base directory with the follow Makefile:

	INFILES = $(shell find . -name "*.mdwn")
	OUTFILES = $(INFILES:.mdwn=.html)

	all: $(OUTFILES)

	%.html: %.mdwn footer.inc header.inc style.css
		m4 -PEIinc header.inc > $@
		markdown $< >> $@
		cat footer.inc >> $@

	clean:
		rm -f $(OUTFILES)

	PHONY: all clean

Now simply run `make` to generate your site.
